                <h4 data-uuid="dc9683cc7dc94006b5b2029f8b57434e">Main Idea</h4>
                <p data-uuid="afa29d473ae546c187e5f72e412410e0" class="main-idea">The
                    Greeks and Romans established new forms of government.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="684425298837481ea7941d676f5158a8">Greek
                    and Roman Influences</h2>
                <div data-uuid="85aa33a89aee4d589e2752e556f904fc" class="yellow-star-yellow-bar"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
