                <h2 data-uuid="fe8643fefa2c4a469b58a54ebe63673c">Democracy and Republic</h2>
                <p data-uuid="9ec75a075cd1470a9f56b4383e3d9ce0"></p>
                <p class="intro" data-uuid="2bc4b8874b5b4ccb8a35cad1e6ad2ff8">Direct democracies and republics are similar forms of government in which the people rule. There are some slight differences, though.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
